    "The region detection module is used to extract the feature and location of the disease area as the input of the caption generation module.",
    "The parameters for all comparison and ablation experiments are shown in Table 6.",
    "The second stage of the DIC-Transformer is trained and tested on NVIDIA P100-16G with CUDA 11.3 using Python 3.8 and PyTorch 1.10 on Ubuntu 18.04.",
    "Additionally, the Detectron2 version used is v0.6, and the MMDetection version is 2.25.1.",
    "We mainly evaluate three tasks: object detection task, image caption generation task, and image classification task."
